<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="spread-v">spread <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /spred/    美 /spred/  </p>
<p>(spread, spread)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>伸开；打开；铺开：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The bird spread its wings.
鸟儿展开翅膀。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She spread her arms and the child ran towards her.
她张开双臂，孩子向她跑去。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>spread a cloth on a table
在桌上铺一块布</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>传播；(使) 蔓延；(使) 流传：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Advertising <strong>spread</strong> quickly <strong>throughout</strong> the eighteenth century.
广告在18世纪迅速传播。</p><footer>2011 全国</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When the stars say something silly, there is always the Internet to spread the news in minutes.
当明星们说了愚蠢的话，总会成为新闻在互联网上立刻传播开来。</p><footer>2013 北京改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She is the sort of woman <strong>to</strong> <strong>spread</strong> sunshine to people through her smile.
她是那种用微笑给别人带来阳光的女人。</p><footer>2010 安徽</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>覆盖；(使) 分布：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The desert spreads for hundreds of miles.
沙漠绵延数百英里。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He always <strong>spread</strong> his energy <strong>across</strong> many goals, so he got nothing at last.
他总是把精力分散在许多目标上，最后一无所获。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>(被) 涂开；(被) 敷开：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>spread</strong> butter <strong>on</strong> pieces of bread
在面包片上涂黄油</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If the paint is too thick, it will not <strong>spread evenly</strong>.
油漆如果太稠就涂不均匀。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="spread-out">spread out</h3>
<p>1.<strong>伸展；摊开；分散：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The general spread out a map to command his army.
将军铺开地图指挥部队。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The searchers spread out to cover the area faster.
搜索人员分散开来，以便于更快地搜索该地区。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The idea started in Standlake and has <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (传开) throughout the country.  （2008 陕西）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. spread  </p></div>